    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进 Kinpath 的世界，一群勇敢的小青蛙开始了成长、探索和传承的旅程。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/c8e233aa8a140a0fcbce6b8781a3bb07.avif?t=1764239025\" width=600 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的青蛙的冒险制定路线并塑造它们的命运。当他们穿越不同的地点时，你的小英雄会变得更强大，获得新技能并发现宝藏。<br><br>他们会钻研魔法，拥抱盗贼的敏捷，还是像坚韧的战士一样坚定不移？旅程由您来计划！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/2ea00ee481e7885ca7f0909b6f0d9d56.poster.avif?t=1764239025\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/2ea00ee481e7885ca7f0909b6f0d9d56.webm?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/2ea00ee481e7885ca7f0909b6f0d9d56.mp4?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/0a060787874428b97b05d4991d46596d.avif?t=1764239025\" width=600 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都会遇到新的敌人。观看您的青蛙利用一路上收集的技能和物品应对这些挑战。他们的成功取决于您在规划他们的道路时所做的选择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/4199929c5635df97352a00d56dd34f4c.poster.avif?t=1764239025\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/4199929c5635df97352a00d56dd34f4c.webm?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/4199929c5635df97352a00d56dd34f4c.mp4?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/8cf615fb659a64aa83c7185c9cba6eb9.avif?t=1764239025\" width=600 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引导你的青蛙穿过不同的地点，一点一点地揭开地图。踏上任务来发展你的技能、收集资源并塑造你的角色的故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/8f6a1b9c6ecc86c894bcb4f1c590530b.poster.avif?t=1764239025\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/8f6a1b9c6ecc86c894bcb4f1c590530b.webm?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039970/extras/8f6a1b9c6ecc86c894bcb4f1c590530b.mp4?t=1764239025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
